title: The Voice's RaeLynn gets enganged to longtime beau
text:
*Washington D.C., Oct. 14(ANI): It's celebration time for 'The Voice's' former contestant RaeLynn as her longtime boyfriend Josh Davis recently popped the question to her.*
Washington D.C., Oct. 14(ANI): It's celebration time for 'The Voice's' former contestant RaeLynn as her longtime boyfriend Josh Davis recently popped the question to her. The team Blake Shelton member tweeted, "Best night of my life" and and also shared a sweet collage of photos showing the proposal as it went down, reports E! Online. RaeLynn captioned the picture, "Of course I start dancing after he asks me to be his wife." Later, she also shared a close up picture with her fiance in which she is seen flaunting her engagement ring and captioned it, "I love you @Josh_Davis_18 cheers to forever" (ANI) Â»
